urlText: Changes to M92 Parramatta to Sutherland bus route
content:

  • 920 Parramatta-Bankstown
  • 960 Bankstown-Sutherland
Passengers travelling the full length of the route (Parramatta to Sutherland), will need to change buses at Bankstown.
  • 920 services depart from Bankstown Station Stand E
  • 960 services depart from Bankstown Station Stand B
All other stops remain the same.
 
For more information see the news story.
 
This change will improve journey time and reliability for passengers and will allow drivers to complete other routes impacted by driver shortages.
 
Plan your trip with Trip Planner or transport apps before you travel.

urlText: Wentworth Point diversions during BBB Fun Run
content:

urlText: Bus diversions for Spring Carnival race days at Randwick
content:
Bus stop closures will be in place during Spring Carnival race days at Royal Randwick Racecourse. Routes 339, 373 and 374 will use alternative stops on the below dates and times.
 
The bus stop on Darley Road opposite Randwick TAFE (203144) will be closed from 9am to 7pm each day on Saturdays 16 Sep, 30 Sep, 14 Oct, 21 Oct, 28 Oct 2023 and Tuesday 7 Nov 2023. Passengers can use the alternative bus stop nearby on Darley Road at Centennial Park Main Gate (203145).
 
On Saturday 14 Oct only, the bus stop at the racecourse on Alison Rd, Australian Turf Club (203142) will be closed from 5pm to 8pm. Shuttle buses to Central will be operating from this stop instead.
 
Passengers catching route 339 buses can use the alternative stop nearby on Darley Rd (2031108). For route 373 passengers can use the stop Moore Park Busway after Alison Rd (203348) and for route 374 use the alternative stop nearby on Alison Rd before Doncaster Ave (203143).
 
Check signs at stops for alternative stop locations and allow extra travel time.
